  "content": "<p data-pid=\"MCiB7EMB\">在专注的练习（例如<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z9uHnUB5sQeGcEmmmqEGqBV\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">有目的的练习，来自 Ericsson 和 Pool</a><sup data-text=\"有目的的练习，来自 Ericsson 和 Pool\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929184759650706472\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>）面前，我们的肌肉和神经系统展现出惊人的可塑性。</p><ul><li data-pid=\"dOMfDssY\">(Ericsson and Pool, 2016, p. 29, 34, 42)<br/></li><ul><li data-pid=\"_ZVatorm\">连续俯卧撑的世界纪录是 <b>10,507 </b>个。</li><li data-pid=\"POOO0m0s\">引体向上的世界纪录是在 <b>12 小时</b>内完成 <b>4,654 </b>个。</li><li data-pid=\"BmCCdoLE\">伦敦的出租车司机要熟记 <b>25000 </b>条街道。</li><li data-pid=\"GqswaOGN\">专业小提琴家能以不可思议的速度，以亚毫米级的精度移动双手。</li></ul></ul><p data-pid=\"2P99ZMz5\">相关概念：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zYNUt6G8oBJBzzUQkM6n35N\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">许多领域的精湛技艺标准已急剧提升</a><sup data-text=\"许多领域的精湛技艺标准已急剧提升\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929250371013964607\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>。</p><hr/><h2><b>参考文献</b></h2><p data-pid=\"68WuBVgb\">Ericsson, A., &amp; Pool, R. (2016).<i>Peak: Secrets from the New Science of Expertise</i>(1 edition). Eamon Dolan/Houghton Mifflin Harcourt. <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zEwJDpZiu1YQoXYznxioznL\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Peak - Ericsson and Pool</a></p><h2><br/>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"ffzgEUpg\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929250371013964607\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">许多领域的精湛技艺标准已急剧提升</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"a1kSLiu9\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"Yu6lrJBQ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 gemini-2.5-pro，校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zpV3kntVjEmJ3PLC2ufDJU\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Human physical and cognitive capacity can be expanded surprisingly far with practice</a></blockquote>",
